The root of the issue is probably `app/app_procs.c`, lines 676-679 (as of bc89e98e):

```
        if (!filename) {
          g_printerr (_("Filename conversion failed: %s\n"), filenames[i]);
          continue;
        }
```

Normally, Dia would continue to the next filename (`++i;`, line 697) after processing one, but this is not done here — hence the endless loop.

Suggested fix:

```
        if (!filename) {
          g_printerr (_("Filename conversion failed: %s\n"), filenames[i]);
          ++i;
          continue;
        }
```
